descriptionHtml:
!!!!This is not completed in anyway shape or form!!!!
Please feel free to download this, explore it, let me know what you think. This is my first time using the Creation Kit, any tips/tricks/suggestions would be greatly appreciated.

No DLC required, only an updated version of Skyrim is required.
This marks the beginning of a massive undertaking to create a large-scale mod. I have not created a way to enter the dungeon in the game world, therefore the only way to get into the dungeon is by using console commands.

To do so follow these steps:
1) Load a Character in Skyrim
2)Press the Tilde(`), the key next to 1
3)Type "coc blackraindungeon" without the quotation marks.
author: Dylan Mitchell
